{"tha-ap365:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap365:0.2":"Mandaravapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap365:0.3":"Bhisamulaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap365:1.1":"“Phusso namasi sambuddho, ","tha-ap365:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap365:1.3":"Vivekakamo sabbannu, ","tha-ap365:1.4":"aganchi mama santike. ","tha-ap365:2.1":"Tasmim cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap365:2.2":"mahakarunike jine; ","tha-ap365:2.3":"Bhisamulalam paggayha, ","tha-ap365:2.4":"buddhasetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap365:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap365:3.2":"yam bhisamadadim tada; ","tha-ap365:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap365:3.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap365:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap365:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap365:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap365:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhisamulaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap365:6.1":"Bhisamulaladayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}